PHP MVC-Framework

Router
You can add your routes in `app/routes.php`:
```php
$app->router->add(
    "/path", 
    function() {
        // your function();
    },
    ["servermethod1", "servermethod2"]
);
```
```php
$app->router->get(
    "/path2", 
    [Path\To\Class::class, "method"]
);
```
```php
$app->router->get(
    "path3/{param}", 
    [Path\To\Class::class, "method"]
);
```

Website is started due to Application class


